== 情节 ==
小祖（凯特·哈德森饰）是一个刚从戒毒所出来的毒贩。在祖母去世后，她发现自己成为患有自闭症、同父异母妹妹小悅（玛蒂·齐格勒饰）的唯一监护人。小祖勉勉強強地擔負这一新的责任，但很快她遇到了一名叫作埃博（小莱斯利·奥多姆飾）的鄰居；他帮助小祖照顾好妹妹。奇幻的音乐片段發生在主人公的内心，展现了她对世界的看法。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Tim Ferriss Show Transcripts: Sia — The Alchemy of Blockbuster Songs, Billions of Views, and the Face You’ve Never Seen (#452)|url=https://tim.blog/2020/08/13/sia-transcript/|accessdate=|author=|date=|first=|work=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220311214909/https://tim.blog/2020/08/13/sia-transcript/|archivedate=2022-03-11|quote=Then inside of her head takes place all these musicals where she’s unburdened by any of her physical disabilities, the tics and the pain.}}</ref>

