== 背景与发展 ==
[[希雅|希雅]]在2015年[[威尼斯电影节|威尼斯电影节上]]宣布了這一电影项目，並稱電影將由[[梅狄·齊格勒|麦迪·齐格勒]]主演。麦迪·齐格勒曾出演过希雅与Daniel Askill<ref name="BBC">{{Cite news|title=Sia to direct film starring young muse Maddie Ziegler|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-34185890|accessdate=2015-09-10|work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|date=2015-09-08|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150911084006/http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-34185890|archivedate=2015-09-11}}</ref><ref name="Tewari">{{Cite news|author=Tewari|first=Nidhi|title='Elastic Heart' Singer Sia to Make a Film Titled 'Sister' with Her Muse Maddie Zeigler|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/elastic-heart-singer-sia-make-film-titled-sister-her-muse-maddie-zeigler-2088277|accessdate=2015-09-10|work=[[International_Business_Times|International Business Times]]|date=2015-09-09|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925194259/http://www.ibtimes.com/elastic-heart-singer-sia-make-film-titled-sister-her-muse-maddie-zeigler-2088277|archivedate=2015-09-25}}; [http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/7263981/sia-releases-captivating-cheap-thrills-video-featuring-maddie-ziegler "Sia Releases Captivating 'Cheap Thrills' Video Featuring Maddie Ziegler"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160910215333/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/7263981/sia-releases-captivating-cheap-thrills-video-featuring-maddie-ziegler|date=2016-09-10}}, ''Billboard'', March 21, 2016; and Murphy, Desiree [http://www.etonline.com/news/197320_maddie_ziegler_rocks_black_wig_rainbow_face_paint_sia_the_greatest_music_video_orlando_victims_tribute "Maddie Ziegler Rocks a Black Wig, Rainbow Face Paint in Sia's Haunting Tribute Video to Orlando Victims"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170417120743/http://www.etonline.com/news/197320_maddie_ziegler_rocks_black_wig_rainbow_face_paint_sia_the_greatest_music_video_orlando_victims_tribute/|date=2017-04-17}}, ETonline.com, 6 September 2016</ref>共同执导的一系列音乐录影带，她曾在希雅的许多现场表演中跳舞。<ref>Lipshutz, Jason. [http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/7556901/sia-live-review-2016 "Sia Remains an Essential Live Performer in 2016"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161123161157/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/7556901/sia-live-review-2016|date=2016-11-23}}, ''Billboard'', October 26, 2016</ref>在2014年创作了《[[水晶吊灯_(歌曲)|Chandelier]]》的MV后，希雅认为自己「很擅长」做导演，「觉得自己更勇敢了」。影片的剧本是由希雅和童书作家达拉斯·克莱顿根据她在2007年写的一个单页故事共同创作的。<ref>{{Cite news|author=Anderson|first=Ariston|title=Venice: Sia Explains Why She's Directing Her Maddie Ziegler Screenplay|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/venice-sia-says-film-starring-820853|accessdate=2015-09-18|publisher=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2016-09-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150911054358/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/venice-sia-says-film-starring-820853|archivedate=2015-09-11}}</ref>希雅很享受这个创作过程，并指出导演和写歌之间有相似之处。

这个项目原本是作为一部非音乐电影来构思的，后来被写成了音乐剧，由希雅演唱歌曲，希雅经常合作的Ryan Heffington进行编舞。<ref>Harding, Laura. [https://www.independent.ie/style/celebrity/celebrity-news/kate-hudson-backs-sia-as-a-director-after-musical-collaboration-36734219.html "Kate Hudson backs Sia as a director after musical collaboration"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180703221119/https://www.independent.ie/style/celebrity/celebrity-news/kate-hudson-backs-sia-as-a-director-after-musical-collaboration-36734219.html|date=2018-07-03}}, ''Independent'', March 22, 2018</ref><ref name="Aron">Aron, Hillel. [https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/sia-face-songs-chandelier-maddie-ziegler-712691 "How Sia Saved Herself"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180824162737/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/sia-face-songs-chandelier-maddie-ziegler-712691/|date=2018-08-24}}, ''[[滾石_(雜誌)|Rolling Stone]]'', August 24, 2018</ref>该片最初的名称为《妹妹（Sister）》，后来改名为《幸福剛剛好（Music）》。凯特·哈德森和小莱斯利·奥多姆加盟齐格勒担任联合主演。<ref>Puente, Maria. [https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/2018/04/06/kate-hudson-expecting-baby-no-3-details-worst-morning-sickness-her-life/493887002 "Kate Hudson expecting baby No. 3, details worst morning sickness of her life"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180620224435/https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/2018/04/06/kate-hudson-expecting-baby-no-3-details-worst-morning-sickness-her-life/493887002/|date=2018-06-20}}, ''USA Today'', April 6, 2018</ref>该片于2017年中拍摄。<ref>Reiher, Andrea. [https://www.popsugar.co.uk/beauty/Why-Did-Kate-Hudson-Cut-Her-Hair-44480690 "The Surprising Reason Kate Hudson Cut All Her Hair Off"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.popsugar.co.uk/beauty/Why-Did-Kate-Hudson-Cut-Her-Hair-44480690 |date=20180409051515 }}, PopSugar, 14 January 2018</ref>当时，齐格勒只有14岁。<ref>[https://news.yahoo.com/maddie-ziegler-155043271.html "Who is Maddie Ziegler?"] {{Wayback|url=https://news.yahoo.com/maddie-ziegler-155043271.html |date=20210122055949 }}, Yahoo.com, November 11, 2020