== 反响 ==

=== 票房 ===
在澳大利亚，《幸福剛剛好》上映首周末的总票房为28.6万美元<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Dry is Back at Number 1|url=https://numero.co/reports/2021/01/18/the-dry-is-back-at-number-1|date=2021-01-18|url-status=live|access-date=2021-01-18|website=Numero|archive-date=2021-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210706040849/https://numero.co/reports/2021/01/18/the-dry-is-back-at-number-1}}</ref>，首周全周票房为44.6万美元<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Dry Takes The Weekly Top Spot in Australia|url=https://numero.co/reports/2021/01/21/the-dry-takes-the-weekly-top-spot-in-australia|date=2021-01-21|access-date=2021-01-21|website=Numero|archive-date=2021-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129142318/https://numero.co/reports/2021/01/21/the-dry-takes-the-weekly-top-spot-in-australia}}</ref>。

